    "en": {
      "name": "Lollipo\u2606Yummy",
      "effect": "If you control a Link-1 monster or a Level 2 Synchro Monster, you can Special Summon this card (from your hand). You can only Special Summon \"Lollipo\u2606Yummy\" once per turn this way. If this card is Normal or Special Summoned: You can target 1 card in your opponent's GY; shuffle it into the Deck, or, if this card was Special Summoned by a Synchro Monster's effect, you can banish that card instead. You can only use this effect of \"Lollipo\u2606Yummy\" once per turn.",
      "official": false
    },
